The paper focuses on incorporating knowledge graph into recommender system, which is a common topic in information retrieval (cs.IR) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also proposes a new recommendation model, which involves joint training with a knowledge graph completion model, indicating the relevance to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and databases (cs.DB). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of natural language processing techniques, suggesting a possible connection to computational linguistics (cs.CL).
